  "detailed_description": "<h1>Become part of the development</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/42b807c9cfbb1422fcb2875076fa6b78.poster.avif?t=1717413379\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/42b807c9cfbb1422fcb2875076fa6b78.webm?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/42b807c9cfbb1422fcb2875076fa6b78.mp4?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get ready for a world of adventure! Slay Together offers challenging gameplay, deep crafting systems, and various customization options. Explore a vast world filled with dangerous monsters and dungeons. Are you ready to start your journey?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The grind</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/8505327628c18176536843b91635111b.poster.avif?t=1717413379\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/8505327628c18176536843b91635111b.webm?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/8505327628c18176536843b91635111b.mp4?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In Slay Together, progress is key. Level up by grinding through monsters, improve your equipment, collect achievements, and climb up the leaderboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crafting & Upgrading</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/776ddfa1d594ee137c28d284f1d6eae3.poster.avif?t=1717413379\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/776ddfa1d594ee137c28d284f1d6eae3.webm?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/776ddfa1d594ee137c28d284f1d6eae3.mp4?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Crafting and upgrading your equipment is everything. Collect ores, plants, and special materials from defeated enemies to craft weapons, armor, and other equipment items.  With a wide range of crafting options available, you can create unique items that suit your playstyle and help you stand out from other players.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play and slay together</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/3e34082ddf00b3c99bd5a7f332d50811.poster.avif?t=1717413379\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/3e34082ddf00b3c99bd5a7f332d50811.webm?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/3e34082ddf00b3c99bd5a7f332d50811.mp4?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Group up with your friends to level up faster and defeat strong enemies and bosses.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/42b807c9cfbb1422fcb2875076fa6b78.poster.avif?t=1717413379\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/42b807c9cfbb1422fcb2875076fa6b78.webm?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/42b807c9cfbb1422fcb2875076fa6b78.mp4?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get ready for a world of adventure! Slay Together offers challenging gameplay, deep crafting systems, and various customization options. Explore a vast world filled with dangerous monsters and dungeons. Are you ready to start your journey?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The grind</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/8505327628c18176536843b91635111b.poster.avif?t=1717413379\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/8505327628c18176536843b91635111b.webm?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/8505327628c18176536843b91635111b.mp4?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In Slay Together, progress is key. Level up by grinding through monsters, improve your equipment, collect achievements, and climb up the leaderboard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crafting & Upgrading</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/776ddfa1d594ee137c28d284f1d6eae3.poster.avif?t=1717413379\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/776ddfa1d594ee137c28d284f1d6eae3.webm?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/776ddfa1d594ee137c28d284f1d6eae3.mp4?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Crafting and upgrading your equipment is everything. Collect ores, plants, and special materials from defeated enemies to craft weapons, armor, and other equipment items.  With a wide range of crafting options available, you can create unique items that suit your playstyle and help you stand out from other players.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play and slay together</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/3e34082ddf00b3c99bd5a7f332d50811.poster.avif?t=1717413379\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/3e34082ddf00b3c99bd5a7f332d50811.webm?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/892510/extras/3e34082ddf00b3c99bd5a7f332d50811.mp4?t=1717413379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Group up with your friends to level up faster and defeat strong enemies and bosses.",
